{
  "title": "O maolahay a mafekac ko Pangcah",
  "titleCh": "熱愛賽跑的阿美族",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "阿美族人是熱愛跑步的民族。每年豐年祭的前一個月，阿美族部落都會舉辦賽跑，因為長老們想瞭解年輕人的體力。因此，頭目召集部落族人在運動場舉行賽跑，依照不同的年齡層分級比賽。",
      "ab": "O halifekacay ko Pangcah a finacadan, i’ayaw no kailisinan to cecay a folad i, ira ko pidemak no niyaro’ to kalalifet a mafekac; nawhani, mafana’ay ko kalas no niyaro’ to cedi^ no kapah, orasaka, pasa’opoen no tomok ko kasaselal no niyaro’ i piondoan a potal a palalifet a mafekac.",
